://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Maria Rockley was born in 1402, in Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England. She had at least 1 son with William Annabel. She died after 1460, in Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1402–after 1460":"1402–pärast 1460","1400–1461":"1400–1461","1460–1501":"1460–1501","1402–1460":"1402–1460","1402":"1402","1501":"1501","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","1461":"1461","after 1460":"pärast 1460","1460":"1460","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England":"Dunstable, Bedfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1402–after 1460":"1402–1460 jälkeen","1400–1461":"1400–1461","1460–1501":"1460–1501","1402–1460":"1402–1460","1402":"1402","1501":"1501","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","1461":"1461","after 1460":"1460 jälkeen","1460":"1460","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England":"Dunstable, Bedfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1402–after 1460":"1402–après 1460","1400–1461":"1400–1461","1460–1501":"1460–1501","1402–1460":"1402–1460","1402":"1402","1501":"1501","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","1461":"1461","after 1460":"après 1460","1460":"1460","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England":"Dunstable, Bedfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Maria Rockley est née en 1402, à Dunstable, Bedfordshire, Angleterre. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William Annabel. Elle est décédée après 1460, à Dunstable, Bedfordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1402–after 1460":"1402–nach 1460","1400–1461":"1400–1461","1460–1501":"1460–1501","1402–1460":"1402–1460","1402":"1402","1501":"1501","1455":"1455","1400":"1400","1461":"1461","after 1460":"nach 1460","1460":"1460","England":"England, United Kingdom","Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England":"Dunstable, Bedfordshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Maria Rockley wurde 14